cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM. 

The paper deals with the problem of sketch segmentation and labeling using deep learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves sketch-based modeling, which falls under the category of cs.GR (Graphics). The use of deep neural networks for transfer learning and post-processing involves techniques from cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper also involves 3D modeling, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia).
